title: when you dominate a m7 championship zed and he calls your champ "braindead"

replies.body:
I destroyed a Darius one trick on Morde and he said Morde was broken...
https://i.imgur.com/vaL29J7.png[]
Well he has a point. Why? Because Zed is a braindead champion too and the only way to kill a braindead champion in below gold is to pick another braindead champion.
I make this same face when I get a first time Mid Laner who happens to miss the half million asol mastery points before the game starts and plays aggro.
